data.name: PagePrintSettings
desc: These properties describe the way the XPagePrintable interface prints the page on one printer page.

properties.name: BottomMargin
desc: contains the right margin of the printer page.

properties.name: HoriMargin
desc: contains the margin between the rows of printed pages.

properties.name: IsLandscape
desc: defines if the printer page is used in landscape format.

properties.name: LeftMargin
desc: contains the left margin of the printer page.

properties.name: PageColumns
desc: contains the number of pages per printed row of pages.

properties.name: PageRows
desc: contains the number of pages per printed column of pages.

properties.name: RightMargin
desc: contains the right margin of the printer page.

properties.name: TopMargin
desc: contains the top margin of the printer page.

properties.name: VertMargin
desc: contains the margin between the columns of printed pages.
